item.title: Are you honestly going through these pictures trying to find a #quote or #message to match your #feelings? Sweetheart, stop. You will make it through this, trust me. I know it #hurts like hell right now, but you will make it through this #pain. You are #notalone. You are never alone. So stop scrolling, and get back up. Pick up your #crown, and show these bitches you may fall, but nothing can break you. 👊🏻💕 #unbreakable #strength #endurance #JustSayinPage #JustSayin
